{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a responsive boat inspection services section that displays 9 service codes (A through I) in a grid layout. Each service card should include:
    
    - A relevant maritime/boat SVG icon (anchor, rope, water drop, electrical plug, dehumidifier, heater, life vest, boat hull, motor)
    - Service code letter and name as heading
    - Price starting from (e.g., "fra 500 Kr/mnd")
    - Bulleted list of inspection items
    - A placeholder image area for boat/marina photos
    - Hover effects on cards
    
    The section should have:
    - Hero area at top with large placeholder image for marina/boat photo
    - Pricing information section below the service cards
    - Volume discount callout box
    - Fully responsive grid: 3 columns on desktop, 2 columns on tablet, 1 column on mobile
    - Customizable settings for colors, spacing, image sizes
    - Mobile-specific adjustments for text size and card padding
    - Clean, modern design with proper spacing and typography
    
    Include all 9 service codes with their Norwegian names and inspection items:
    KODE A – FORTØYNING (Plassering av båten, Fortøyningstau, Strekkavlastere, Halegatt, Kryssholt, Sjakler, Fendere)
    KODE B – KALLESJE (Fester, Glidelås, Feste bøyler)
    KODE C – VANN INNTREGNING (Vann om bord, Lense pumpe, Selvlens)
    KODE D – LANDSTRØM (Landstrøm, Kabel, Tilkoblingsskap på kai, Tilkobling om bord)
    KODE E – AVFUKTER (Elektriske, Manuelle)
    KODE F – VARME (Varmekilde, Tilkobling)
    KODE G – SIKKERHET OG UTSTYR (Brannslukkere, Redningsvester, Nødbluss, Førstehjelpsutstyr, Båtshake, Gass)
    KODE H – SKROG OG DEKK (Visuell inspeksjon, Luker og ventiler)
    KODE I – MOTOR OG DRIVSTOFF (Påhengsmotor sikret, Drivstoffslanger, Batteritilkobling, Styre wire)
    
    Add pricing details section explaining the monthly inspection pricing, 50% discount for second monthly inspection, and 20% volume discount for 10+ boats per marina., I need to be able to change icon svgs, the pictures in the services needs to line up. horizontally, add a show more button for the bullet points, add a show more text button for the bullet points, add a show more text button if exceeding more thanthree bullet points, make the vis mer button more compact and minimal, These do not work:
    Container width
    Section padding top
    Section padding bottom
    Section padding horizontal, problem with padding controls, Hero image full width no padding, Hero image problem on mobile view, Hero image problem not being full width on both desktop and mobile, Change Hero title colour
    , unique padding for desktop and mobile, I need to be able to change text in each service card, add individual pricing for the services as well
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-boat-inspection-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 0;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100vw;
    left: 50%;
    right: 50%;
    margin-left: -50vw;
    margin-right: -50vw;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.hero_margin_bottom }}px;
    border-radius: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    height: {{ block.settings.hero_height }}px;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-hero-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-hero-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    }

  .ai-boat-inspection-hero-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    max-width: 400px;
    max-height: 300px;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-hero-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient({{ block.settings.overlay_direction }}, {{ block.settings.overlay_color_start }}, {{ block.settings.overlay_color_end }});
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-hero-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-hero-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.hero_title_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.hero_title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-hero-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.hero_subtitle_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.hero_subtitle_size }}px;
    margin: 0;
    opacity: 0.9;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-content-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: {{ block.settings.desktop_padding_top }}px {{ block.settings.desktop_padding_horizontal }}px {{ block.settings.desktop_padding_bottom }}px {{ block.settings.desktop_padding_horizontal }}px;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.container_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-services-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.services_margin_bottom }}px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background_color }};
    border: {{ block.settings.card_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.card_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding }}px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100%;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    border-color: {{ block.settings.card_hover_border_color }};
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.icon_color }};
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.service_title_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.service_title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.price_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.price_size }}px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-items-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-items-{{ ai_gen_id }} ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-items-{{ ai_gen_id }} li {
    color: {{ block.settings.list_text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.list_text_size }}px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    padding-left: 16px;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-items-{{ ai_gen_id }} li:before {
    content: "•";
    color: {{ block.settings.bullet_color }};
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-items-{{ ai_gen_id }} .hidden-items {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-items-{{ ai_gen_id }}.expanded .hidden-items {
    max-height: 300px;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-toggle-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    padding: 4px 0;
    font-size: 12px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    text-align: left;
    width: fit-content;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-toggle-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_text }};
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: auto;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    height: {{ block.settings.service_image_height }}px;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.service_image_border_radius }}px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #f8f9fa;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border: 2px dashed #dee2e6;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-service-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-pricing-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: stretch;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-pricing-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.pricing_bg_color }};
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, {{ block.settings.pricing_padding | divided_by: 16.0 }}rem, 3rem);
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.pricing_border_radius | divided_by: 16.0 }}rem;
    margin: 0;
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.pricing_border_color }};
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    width: min(100%, 34rem);
    max-width: 100%;
    flex: 1 1 clamp(20rem, 32vw, 34rem);
    box-sizing: border-box;
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-pricing-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.pricing_title_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.pricing_title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-pricing-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.pricing_text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.pricing_text_size }}px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: min(100%, 42rem);
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-discount-box-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.discount_bg_color }};
    border: 2px solid {{ block.settings.discount_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.discount_border_radius | divided_by: 16.0 }}rem;
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, {{ block.settings.discount_padding | divided_by: 16.0 }}rem, 3rem);
    text-align: center;
    width: min(100%, 34rem);
    max-width: 100%;
    flex: 1 1 clamp(20rem, 32vw, 34rem);
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-discount-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.discount_title_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.discount_title_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-boat-inspection-discount-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.discount_text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.discount_text_size }}px;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: center;
    width: 100%;
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 990px) {
    .ai-boat-inspection-services-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .ai-boat-inspection-hero-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.hero_title_size }}px * 0.8);
    }

    .ai-boat-inspection-hero-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.hero_subtitle_size }}px * 0.9);
    }

    .ai-boat-inspection-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      height: calc({{ block.settings.hero_height }}px * 0.8);
    }

    .ai-boat-inspection-hero-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 30px 15px;
    }

    .ai-boat-inspection-content-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.tablet_padding_top }}px {{ block.settings.tablet_padding_horizontal }}px {{ block.settings.tablet_padding_bottom }}px {{ block.settings.tablet_padding_horizontal }}px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-boat-inspection-services-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .ai-boat-inspection-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      height: calc({{ block.settings.hero_height }}px * 0.7);
    }

    .ai-boat-inspection-service-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      {% assign mobile_card_padding = block.settings.card_padding | times: 0.8 %}
      padding: {{ mobile_card_padding }}px;
    }

    .ai-boat-inspection-hero-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.hero_title_size }}px * 0.7);
    }

    .ai-boat-inspection-hero-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.hero_subtitle_size }}px * 0.8);
    }

    .ai-boat-inspection-service-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ block.settings.service_title_size }}px * 0.9);
    }

    .ai-boat-inspection-hero-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 20px 10px;
    }

    .ai-boat-inspection-content-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.mobile_padding_top }}px {{ block.settings.mobile_padding_horizontal }}px {{ block.settings.mobile_padding_bottom }}px {{ block.settings.mobile_padding_horizontal }}px;
    }

    {% assign mobile_pricing_padding = block.settings.pricing_padding | times: 0.8 %}
    {% assign mobile_discount_padding = block.settings.discount_padding | times: 0.8 %}

    .ai-boat-inspection-pricing-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: clamp(1.25rem, {{ mobile_pricing_padding | divided_by: 16.0 }}rem, 2.5rem);
    }

    .ai-boat-inspection-discount-box-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: clamp(1.25rem, {{ mobile_discount_padding | divided_by: 16.0 }}rem, 2.5rem);
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 48rem) {
    .ai-boat-inspection-pricing-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: clamp(1.5rem, 6vw, 2.5rem);
      margin: 0 auto clamp(1.5rem, 6vw, 2.5rem);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .ai-boat-inspection-pricing-section-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-boat-inspection-discount-box-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      max-width: min(100%, 34rem);
      width: 100%;
    }

    .ai-boat-inspection-pricing-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-boat-inspection-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  {% if block.settings.hero_image or block.settings.hero_title != blank or block.settings.hero_subtitle != blank %}
    <div class="ai-boat-inspection-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.hero_image %}
        <img
          src="{{ block.settings.hero_image | image_url: width: 1600 }}"
          alt="{{ block.settings.hero_image.alt | escape }}"
          class="ai-boat-inspection-hero-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          loading="lazy"
          width="{{ block.settings.hero_image.width }}"
          height="{{ block.settings.hero_image.height }}"
        >
      {% else %}
        <div class="ai-boat-inspection-hero-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {{ 'hero-apparel-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.hero_title != blank or block.settings.hero_subtitle != blank %}
        <div class="ai-boat-inspection-hero-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <div class="ai-boat-inspection-hero-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% if block.settings.hero_title != blank %}
              <h1 class="ai-boat-inspection-hero-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.hero_title }}</h1>
            {% endif %}
            {% if block.settings.hero_subtitle != blank %}
              <p class="ai-boat-inspection-hero-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.hero_subtitle }}</p>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  {% endif %}

  <div class="ai-boat-inspection-content-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <boat-inspection-services-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-boat-inspection-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-boat-inspection-services-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% assign services = 'A,B,C,D,E,F,G,H,I' | split: ',' %}

        {% for service in services %}
          {% assign service_index = forloop.index0 %}
          {% assign service_name_key = 'service_' | append: service | append: '_name' %}
          {% assign service_items_key = 'service_' | append: service | append: '_items' %}
          {% assign service_image_key = 'service_' | append: service | append: '_image' %}
          {% assign service_icon_key = 'service_' | append: service | append: '_icon_svg' %}
          {% assign service_price_key = 'service_' | append: service | append: '_price' %}

          {% assign service_name = block.settings[service_name_key] %}
          {% assign service_items_text = block.settings[service_items_key] %}
          {% assign service_list = service_items_text | split: '|' %}
          {% assign service_price = block.settings[service_price_key] %}

          <div class="ai-boat-inspection-service-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-boat-inspection-service-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-boat-inspection-service-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% if block.settings[service_icon_key] != blank %}
                  {{ block.settings[service_icon_key] }}
                {% else %}
                  {% case service %}
                    {% when 'A' %}
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="5" r="3"/>
                        <path d="M12 22V8"/>
                        <path d="M5 12H2a10 10 0 0 0 20 0h-3"/>
                      </svg>
                    {% when 'B' %}
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                        <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/>
                        <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/>
                        <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/>
                      </svg>
                    {% when 'C' %}
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M3 12h3l3-9 6 18 3-9h3"/>
                      </svg>
                    {% when 'D' %}
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M12 2v20"/>
                        <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
                      </svg>
                    {% when 'E' %}
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <rect width="20" height="15" x="2" y="7" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                        <polyline points="17,4 12,4 12,7"/>
                      </svg>
                    {% when 'F' %}
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M14 4v10.54a4 4 0 1 1-4 0V4a2 2 0 0 1 4 0Z"/>
                      </svg>
                    {% when 'G' %}
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"/>
                        <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/>
                      </svg>
                    {% when 'H' %}
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M2 20a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8l-7 5V6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12Z"/>
                        <path d="M6 18h.01"/>
                        <path d="M10 18h.01"/>
                      </svg>
                    {% when 'I' %}
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
                        <path d="M12 1v6m0 6v6"/>
                        <path d="m15.5 3.5-1.5 1.5m0 12 1.5 1.5"/>
                        <path d="m8.5 3.5 1.5 1.5m0 12-1.5 1.5"/>
                        <path d="M1 12h6m6 0h6"/>
                        <path d="m3.5 8.5 1.5 1.5m12 0 1.5-1.5"/>
                        <path d="m3.5 15.5 1.5-1.5m12 0 1.5 1.5"/>
                      </svg>
                  {% endcase %}
                {% endif %}
              </div>
              <h3 class="ai-boat-inspection-service-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                KODE {{ service }} – {{ service_name }}
              </h3>
            </div>

            <div class="ai-boat-inspection-service-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-boat-inspection-service-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% if service_price != blank %}
                  fra {{ service_price }} Kr/mnd
                {% else %}
                  fra {{ block.settings.base_price }} Kr/mnd
                {% endif %}
              </div>

              {% if service_items_text != blank %}
